<section xml:id="_code_ligatures">
<title>Code Ligatures</title>
<simpara>Some fonts support source code related ligatures.
We&#8217;ll test these code related ligatures using a test file taken from Nikita Prokopov&#8217;s
<link xl:href="https://github.com/tonsky/FiraCode">Fira Code</link> project.</simpara>
<simpara>First we&#8217;ll test for ligatures inside a source code block.
Here ligatures support could depend on the monospaced font, the backend or the syntax highligher (which may or may not filter contents of the block).</simpara>
